faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戰力單位傑諾斯<br />\n<br />\n永遠用嚟彰顯敵人既強大</blockquote><br />\n要自爆了....對不起...博士"},{"pid":"437bdebc269d37fb65108fb151ce23a194f611f7","tid":433410,"uid":65710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>傑仔出場夠晒型<br />\n但結果唔駛講都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開罐頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戰力單位傑諾斯<br />\n<br />\n永遠用嚟彰顯敵人既強大</blockquote><br />\nONE好似講過傑仔實力係S級入面嚟講都唔算差<br />\n只係佢遇開D怪人太勁<br />\n好似深海王,豪傑,餓狼"},{"pid":"c09e86fa3027136b2ee2606ed9ab4648b14aae0a","tid":433410,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講到咁完美 最後都係俾佢破解咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼鏡仔算係咁 暈咗都叫得切支援</blockquote><br />\n而家講到餓狼係救細路先擋子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個轉變好好，希望之後邦布俾人插腳嘅劇情都會改啦</blockquote><br />\n黎緊救餓狼嘅應該係蜈蚣長老，一個龍級從三個S級實力手上救走餓狼，會合理好多。</blockquote><br />\n我覺得怪人協會救餓狼<br />\n就係想彌補返豪傑既損失<br />\n大家都係識打功夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>豈能在這種地方倒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bfc67f0fa86af5e8c42c033083a74a45eabe0dcc","tid":433410,"uid":36651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T12:01:16.000Z","msg":"又話10月有一拳第二季，係咪已經有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66de36bb5fac790118580d1c960025bcf4eb1dd3","tid":433410,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"